divs: sighting details9 red solid lights floating west to east through the normal n2south flight pattern of dfw airport. 1st hand account was of last seriers of three lights, formation type pattern with lights diming out within a few seconds of each other. i caught series of lights traveling through normal heavy traffic flight pattern of the dallas ft worth airport. typically flights travel north\south but these lights traveled through at west to east. these where not copters, as i have one caught on same video traveling from north to south with faa lights and low alititude. i am former airwing military and have never seen anything like this before. this was seen on friday night septemeber 23, 2011 at 23:20
